OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail under new
OL,4,Cplans to crackdown on pollution
OL,6,FWater company bosses could be banned
OL,7,Ffrom receiving bonuses and even sent
OL,8,Fto prison under proposed UK Government
OL,9,Flaws to combat pollution in rivers,
OL,10,Fseas and lakes.
OL,12,FThe Water (Special Measures) Bill,
OL,13,Fintroduced to the UK Parliament on
OL,14,FWednesday, will hand new powers to
OL,15,FOfwat and the Environment Agency to
OL,16,Ftake action on companies damaging the
OL,17,Fenvironment and failing customers.
