OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail under new
OL,4,Cplans to crackdown on pollution
OL,6,FThe UK Government said the current
OL,7,Fenforcement system is insufficient to
OL,8,Fhold firms accountable for widespread
OL,9,Fillegality in the sector, citing that
OL,10,Fonly three individuals have been
OL,11,Fcriminally prosecuted by the
OL,12,FEnvironment Agency without appeal
OL,13,Fsince privatisation.
OL,15,FUnder the Bill, harsher penalties for
OL,16,Flaw-breaking will be introduced,
OL,17,Fincluding jail sentences of up to two
OL,18,Fyears for executives who fail to
OL,19,Fcooperate or obstruct Environment
OL,20,FAgency and Drinking Water Inspectorate
OL,21,Finvestigations.
