OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail under new
OL,4,Cplans to crackdown on pollution
OL,6,FRegulators will also be empowered to
OL,7,Fban bonus payments to water bosses if
OL,8,Fthey fail to meet high standards to
OL,9,Fprotect the environment, their
OL,10,Fconsumers and their company's finances.
OL,12,FThe proposed laws will apply in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales.
OL,15,FThe new Labour Government has already
OL,16,Fannounced initial measures to tackle
OL,17,Fpollution but this is its first major
OL,18,Fmove to deliver on its manifesto
OL,19,Fpledges to reform the broken water
OL,20,Fsystem.
