OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail under new
OL,4,Cplans to crackdown on pollution
OL,6,FUK Secretary of State for Environment,
OL,7,FFood and Rural Affairs, Steve Reed,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The public are furious that in
OL,9,F21st century Britain, record levels of
OL,10,Fsewage are being pumped into our
OL,11,Frivers, lakes and seas. After years of
OL,12,Fneglect, our waterways are now in an
OL,13,Funacceptable state.
OL,15,F"That is why today I am announcing
OL,16,Fimmediate action to end the
OL,17,Fdisgraceful behaviour of water
OL,18,Fcompanies and their bosses.
