OL,3,CWater bosses could face jail under new
OL,4,Cplans to crackdown on pollution
OL,6,F"Under this government, water
OL,7,Fexecutives will no longer line their
OL,8,Fown pockets whilst pumping out this
OL,9,Ffilth. If they refuse to comply, they
OL,10,Fcould end up in the dock and face
OL,11,Fprison time.
OL,13,F"This Bill is a major step forward in
OL,14,Four wider reform to fix the broken
OL,15,Fwater system. We will outline further
OL,16,Flegislation to fundamentally transform
OL,17,Fhow the water industry is run and
OL,18,Fspeed up the delivery of upgrades to
OL,19,Four sewage infrastructure to clean up
OL,20,Four waterways for good."
